===Nominations===

*1993-94: Hart Trophy (loss to [[Sergei Fedorov]])
*1994-95: Hart Trophy (loss to [[Jaromir Jagr]])

==Transactions==

* 1983 - Drafted by Chicago 199th overall
* 1992 - Traded to Buffalo for [[Stephane Beauregard]] and a fourth round pick ([[Eric Daze]])
* 2001 - Traded to Detroit for [[Vyacheslav Kozlov]], a first round pick in 2002 ([[Jim Slater (hockey player)|Jim Slater]]) and future considerations
* 2004 - Signed as a [[Free agent|UFA]] by Ottawa
* 2006 - Signed as a UFA by Detroit

